{"tid":2192454,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"「黃店中伏記」燒茄子未燒熟真係第一次見...","createTime":"2020-09-07T06:36:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-07T07:48:40.000Z","uid":13361,"like":3,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"52390754edf8e9cc3d25b60ed0bc7200b78f5616","tid":2192454,"uid":13361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T06:36:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bihPrFb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbihPrFb.jpg&h=2a7160d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有一半茄子肉都未熟透（仲係白色）夾唔起<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食咗咁多年串燒真係第一次見 雖然價錢係唔貴 但都唔洗咁求其掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他食物都只是普通 燒蠔無蠔味 芝麻雞翼已經係最好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n旺角某黃店串燒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f801fc463ba10055a725966ac0fcdfe3149d716","tid":2192454,"uid":68490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T06:39:14.000Z","msg":"食何文田某黃店囉<br />\n又貴份量少仲要唔好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d96610bd76eac8b7069ab22c0cb725b1f61d15a0","tid":2192454,"uid":13361,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4f801fc463ba10055a725966ac0fcdfe3149d716","tid":2192454,"uid":68490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T06:39:14.000Z","msg":"食何文田某黃店囉<br />\n又貴份量少仲要唔好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T06:40:44.000Z","msg":"我有一半茄子唔食得 等於我要叫兩條茄子先等於一條<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />應該貴過你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80f8def276eb604d8903d5b931e2b69d97fa27aa","tid":2192454,"uid":32051,"like":20,"dislike":6,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"20